      <title>路透调查显示，由于芯片复苏，韩国一月出口可能连续第四个月增长</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/south-korea-jan-exports-likely-rose-fourth-month-chip-recovery-2024-01-30/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[路透社周二的一项民意调查显示，由于芯片销售增长，韩国 1 月份出口可能连续第四个月增长，受日历影响，整体数据进一步推高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/south-korea-jan-exports-likely-rose-fourth-month-chip-recovery-2024-01-30/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Jan 2024 05:17:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本黑马首相候选人呼吁结束日本央行负利率政策</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/japan-dark-horse-premier-candidate-calls-ending-bojs-negative-rate-policy-2024-01-30/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[执政党重量级人物石破茂表示，日本央行必须立即结束负利率政策，因为该政策通过将借贷成本保持在超低水平，让企业推迟了提高生产率的努力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/japan-dark-horse-premier-candidate-calls-ending-bojs-negative-rate-policy-2024-01-30/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Jan 2024 05:11:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本首相誓言将“尽一切可能”增加家庭收入</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/japan-pm-vows-do-everything-possible-boost-household-income-2024-01-30/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本首相岸田文雄周二表示，日本政府将“尽一切可能”实现实际收入增长，以果断结束通货紧缩。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/japan-pm-vows-do-everything-possible-boost-household-income-2024-01-30/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Jan 2024 05:01:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜耳面临澳大利亚法官的测试，以确定除草剂是否致癌</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/bayer-faces-australian-test-with-judge-decide-whether-weedkiller-caused-cancer-2024-01-30/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚一家法院周二听取了一项集体诉讼的结案陈词，该诉讼指控拜耳生产的除草剂导致癌症，这是澳大利亚首例进入此阶段的此类案件。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/bayer-faces-australian-test-with-judge-decide-whether-weedkiller-caused-cancer-2024-01-30/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Jan 2024 04:53:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国在台商业集团预计下滑，但地缘政治担忧依然较高</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/us-business-group-taiwan-sees-falling-still-high-geopolitical-concerns-2024-01-30/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[台湾美国商会（AmCham）调查的近一半公司认为，地缘政治担忧阻碍了在台湾的扩张或投资，但尽管中国的紧张局势依然存在，这一数字却大幅下降。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/us-business-group-taiwan-sees-falling-still-high-geopolitical-concerns-2024-01-30/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Jan 2024 03:58:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印尼央行称卢比未来将保持稳定</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/indonesia-finmin-says-rupiah-remain-stable-going-forward-2024-01-30/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度尼西亚财政部长 Sri Mulyani Indrawati 周二表示，由于美元走软的压力，卢比汇率将保持稳定，并有走强的趋势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/indonesia-finmin-says-rupiah-remain-stable-going-forward-2024-01-30/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Jan 2024 03:04:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>越南与菲律宾签署南海安全协议</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/vietnam-philippines-seal-deals-south-china-sea-security-2024-01-30/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[越南和菲律宾总统小费迪南德·马科斯在对河内进行国事访问期间宣布，越南和菲律宾周二同意加强海岸警卫队之间的合作，防止南海发生不愉快的事件。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/vietnam-philippines-seal-deals-south-china-sea-security-2024-01-30/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Jan 2024 02:54:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于对中国房地产业的担忧重压，亚洲股市下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-01-30/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亚洲股市周二下跌，受法院下令清算房地产巨头中国恒大的影响，而地缘政治紧张局势加剧支撑了油价，并在美联储会议之前抑制了风险偏好]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-01-30/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Jan 2024 02:47:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>香港特首开始推动新国安法，称香港“等不起”</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/hong-kong-leaders-start-legislative-push-tighten-national-security-laws-2024-01-30/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[香港领导人周二证实，他打算很快通过更严格的国家安全法，以北京 2020 年对香港实施的全面立法为基础，并表示香港“等不起”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/hong-kong-leaders-start-legislative-push-tighten-national-security-laws-2024-01-30/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Jan 2024 02:18:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>电动汽车制造商 VinFast 今年将投资菲律宾</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/ev-maker-vinfast-invest-philippines-this-year-2024-01-30/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[越南电动汽车制造商 VinFast 的母公司 Vingroup 周二在菲律宾总统小费迪南德·马科斯 (Ferdinand Marcos Jr.) 访问期间发布声明称，将在菲律宾开设电动汽车业务网络。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/ev-maker-vinfast-invest-philippines-this-year-2024-01-30/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Jan 2024 02:13:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
